<h3>GET /api/charges</h3>
<div>
  List charges
</div>
<b>Resource URL </b>
<div>
  http://localhost:3000/api/charges
</div>
<b>Example request</b>
<div>
  curl -X GET -H 'Authorization: Bearer auth_token' "http://localhost:3000/api/charges?project_id=10"
  <br/>
  auth_token: jwt token of current user
</div>
